Scheme name: matrix

Status: Provisional

Applications/protocols that use this scheme name:
This scheme name is for use by the Matrix protocol (https://matrix.org/), an
open, decentralised real-time communication protocol.

Contact: Hubert Chathi <hubertc&matrix.org>

Change controller:
Anyone on The Matrix.org Foundation C.I.C's Spec Core Team. The members of the
Team may be found at https://matrix.org/foundation/

References:
The current proposed scheme specification can be found at
https://github.com/matrix-org/matrix-doc/pull/2312 .